Package com.taco.suit_lady.view.ui.content

Class TransitionContentView<P extends javafx.scene.layout.Pane>

java.lang.Object
com.taco.suit_lady.view.ui.content.ContentView<P>
com.taco.suit_lady.view.ui.content.TransitionContentView<P>
public class TransitionContentView<P extends javafx.scene.layout.Pane> extends ContentView<P>
A ContentView that only displays a single content at any given time. The only time in which more than one content can ever be displayed is during a transition.
